def_cn: 牢不可破的;固若金汤的;无法攻取的
def_en: If you describe a building or other place as impregnable, you mean that it cannot be broken into or captured.

def_cn: 不可战胜的;不可撼动的
def_en: If you say that a person or group is impregnable, or their position is impregnable, you think they cannot be defeated by anyone.
